<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="container content-section text-center">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h1>About me</h1>
            <p>I'm a @ViewBag.Age year old IT guy from Langemark, Belgium.</p>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <h4>My experience</h4>
                    <p>
                        I graduated as a Computer & Cyber Crime Professional, a bachelors degree in the Applied Informatics,
                        from the <a href="http://www.howest.be" title="Howest website" target="_blank">Howest</a> University in Bruges (Belgium).
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        In the last year of my education, I was allowed to do an internship as a security auditor at a Belgian SME.
                        During that period, I learned a lot about analyzing corporate networks and how to make them more efficient and secure.
                        It also gave me some real life programming and webdesign experience.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Currently I'm employed at a Belgian company called
                        <a href="http://www.crefius.com" title="Crefius website" target="_blank">Crefius</a>,
                        as a member of their IT Infrastructure team.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <h4>My goals</h4>
                    <p>
                        Since I was a little, I have always wanted to help people and I have always had an interest in the ICT world.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Nowadays I go and combine both things by helping others with problems they're facing,
                        whether they need help choosing or building a new computer or they want me to perform a full checkup of their device.
                    </p>
                    <h5>Some of the things I often do:</h5>
                    <ul style="color: white;list-style: none">
                        <li>Building custom computers (gaming or otherwise) or helping people decide which system(s) to buy</li>
                        <li>Computer security and health check-ups</li>
                        <li>Creating and/or designing websites</li>
                        <li>Creating and/or designing applications</li>
                        <li>Setting up (secure) home or business networks</li>
                        <li>A lot of other stuff</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12">
                    <h5>My latest resume can be viewed <a href="~/Content/files/CV-Arne.pdf" title="CV" target="_blank">here</a> <small>(For the moment it's only in Dutch)</small></h5>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

